Private Sub Form_Load()
  On Error GoTo SubError
   Dim cat As Recordset
   Dim AddAt As Integer
   Set cat = CurrentDb().OpenRecordset("Categories", dbOpenDynaset)
  ' Cats.AddItem "ALL", 0   'Access 2000 does not have add for listbox
   Cats.RowSource = "ALL "
   AddAt = 1
   With cat
   If Not .EOF Then
     Do While Not .EOF
 '      Cats.AddItem !NCAT, AddAt
       Cats.RowSource = Cats.RowSource & ";" & !NCAT ' This works for access 2000
       AddAt = AddAt + 1
       .MoveNext
     Loop
   End If
   End With
   Exit Sub
SubError:
   MsgBox "Error in FormLoad (Ranking Selector) " & Err.Description
End Sub
